			<tr>
				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Obtaining Your Disciplines<a name="18008"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jan 30 04 11:48 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I am putting this here since I needed to ask someone how to get my first disc a few days ago.
<br />

<br />
The bard disciplines are purchased in book form from an NPC in the EC Tunnel, Almon Juliao.  
<br />

<br />
The Bard disciplines (from the skills link along the left side of this awesome website) are:
<br />

<br />
Disciplines
<br />
 
<br />
Level   Discipline       Duration       Reuse 
<br />
51      Resistance      5 minutes     60 minutes 
<br />
54      Fearless         11 seconds   60 minutes 
<br />
55      Deftdance      15 seconds   72 minutes 
<br />
60      Puretone        4 minutes      72 minutes 
<br />

<br />

<br />
All 4 books are 2 cp ea.  After buying the book, you go to any Bard GM trainer and turn in the discipline book you are eligible for and he trains you.
<br />

<br />
Then you can type / disc (name of discipline) to activate it.  Best thing is to make a hotkey of course.
<br />

<br />
Please add any other information I missed on this.  As a point of interest, the resistance disc seems to only have a 30 min timer.  I can't comment on the others &lt;yet&gt;.
<br />

<br />
Thanks
<br />

<br />
Badji</span></td>
